            <div type="transcript" id="F267A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Rearrange a &quot;Wife's&quot; Affection!</l>
                    <l>When they dislocate my Brain!  </l>
                    <l>Amputate my freckled Bosom!  </l>
                    <l>Make me bearded like a man!  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Blush, my spirit, in thy<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Fastness -</l>
                    <l>Blush, my unacknowledged<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 clay - </l>
                    <l>Seven years of troth have<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 taught thee </l>
                    <l>More than Wifehood ever may!  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Love that never leaped <app type="emendation"><lem>its</lem><rdg>it&#x27;s</rdg></app>
 socket - </l>
                    <l>Trust <app type="emendation"><lem>entrenched</lem><rdg>intrenched</rdg></app>
 in narrow<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 pain -</l>
                    <l>Constancy thro' fire - awarded - </l>
                    <l>Anguish - bare of anodyne!<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Burden - borne so far<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 triumphant - </l>
                    <l>None suspect me of the crown, </l>
                    <l>For I wear the &quot;Thorns&quot; till <em>Sunset</em> -</l>
                    <l>Then - my Diadem put on.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Big my Secret but it's<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 <em>bandaged</em> - </l>
                    <l>It will never get away </l>
                    <l>Till the Day <app type="emendation"><lem>its</lem><rdg>it&#x27;s</rdg></app>
 Weary Keeper </l>
                    <l>Leads it through the Grave<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to thee.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
